  "body": "- [ ] I've asked for help in the [Truffle Gitter](http://gitter.im/Consensys/truffle) before filing this issue.\n\n---\n## Issue\n\n`truffle watch` crashes if the contracts currently do not compile\n## Steps to Reproduce\n\nrun `truffle watch`, edit a contract with a mistake that prevent compiling, save\n## Expected Behavior\n\nThe error is displayed, watching keeps going though.\n## Actual Results\n\nAn unhandled exception is throw:\n\n```\ntruffle/node_modules/solidity-parser/index.js:39\n      throw e;\n```\n## Additional note\n\nThe exception has to be caught probably in \n`truffle/lib/profiler.js:134:36`\n",
